Class User

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.hadoop.fs.swift.auth.entities.User

public class User
extends Object

Describes user entity in Keystone In different Swift installations User is represented differently. To avoid any JSON deserialization failures this entity is ignored. THIS FILE IS MAPPED BY JACKSON TO AND FROM JSON. DO NOT RENAME OR MODIFY FIELDS AND THEIR ACCESSORS.
